      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65f22151ad0d3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65f221a3b56aa.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65edf9885b72e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65edf8dce8a2a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65edfa30dff66.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655b63355b722.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655b63dab54cf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655b63c5becb3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655b62cce92f9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/655b62db7b614.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; UltraCam 2.6, climbing speed and More&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Updates are slowed down for the moment, broke my leg and undergoing surgery recovery. Won't be able to walk until 2025.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Climbing Speed Between ALL FPS&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Climbing Jump Between ALL FPS&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Ladder Climbing Speed Between ALL FPS&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Ladder Animations ending abruptly at higher than 55 FPS&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tweak&lt;/em&gt;: Removed Ladder Climbing FPS Lock&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tweak&lt;/em&gt;: Removed the ability to change FOV with the controller while outside of FreeCam&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;ULTRACAM - Features - Supported Vers. 1.1.0, 1.1.1, 1.1.2, 1.2.0, 1.2.1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hybrid-FPS (480FPS cap) (NEW) - Dynamically adjusts and also fixes physic issues.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Freecam&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Sequencer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;FOV (20-120) ANY NUMBER. (Real Time Control) (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fog Reduction&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Emu Scale (Match to Emulator)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Internal Resolution (Up to 8K!) (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Shadow Resolution (Up to 8K!) (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Quality Improvements (Disable FSR, Dynamic Resolution) (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DisableFXAA (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Disable Depth of Field (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Camera Speed Multipliers. (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hide UI (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;AutoHide UI (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;MenuFPSLock (NEW)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;MovieFPS (NEW)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Time and Weather Control (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Benchmarks (NEW)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Teleportation (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Heap Settings RSDB and GameTextures (NEW)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;ULTRACAM 3.0 EARLY ACCESS VERSION SOON AVAILABLE IN &lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/post/UltraCam-2-0-DOWNLOAD-BETA-1-V7V7S6CJQ" target="_blank"&gt;KOFI&lt;/a&gt;. The next major release is potentially going to take months, this MOD has taken over 1000+ hours of development time.&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 class="SelectedElement"&gt;Want to keep up with the project development? Join &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/the-way-of-the-wind-1111435904687550587"&gt;DISCORD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;New Console&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Full control of almost every feature in real time. (Shadows, Resolution, FPS etc)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Future Actor spawning functionality. (April-May)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Full in-game UI (Imagine reshade but for TOTK)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lots of new gameplay tweaks (passive health regen out of combat!)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Potential Enemy and Weapon Randomizer (built in)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Slow motion/Fast Motion and Freeze AI.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Entity control, let's you take control of different enemies!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Port of UltraCam to DFPS.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;TO BE RELEASED WHEN ITS FINISHED.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;FOR FULL CONTEXT CHECK OUT BOTH VIDEOS!&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Video &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H7vza53cNzc" target="_blank"&gt;One&lt;/a&gt; is a breakdown of how to use the Freecam (OLD)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Video &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/vEAJkdoI_FI" target="_blank"&gt;Two&lt;/a&gt; is an amazing Trailer Cinematic using the Freecam by Gossip Geist. &lt;3 Really recommend checking it out!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;I LOVE THIS, HOW CAN I HELP THE DEVELOPMENT?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;You can support me on my &lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/maxlastbreath#" target="_blank"&gt;KO-FI.&lt;/a&gt; and also get access to new features in EA!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;WHAT DOES THIS MOD DO?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;The primary focus of this mod is to improve the game's Quality and Visuals as well as the framerate at which the game runs and how well it runs at higher FPS. (Yes this does run better then any other DFPS mods.)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The mod also allows you to enter a Freecam mode. Which also allows for the creation of cinematic keyframes and the teleportation of Link.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also FIXES LODS, SSAO by being able to increase the internal resolution.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also fixes the shadow flickering. By being able to increase shadows up to 8K.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also comes with various FPS fixes that Fixes the following: &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Menu Speeds, Bow Speed, Throw Weapon Speed, Map Menu Speed, Movie Speeds, Dynamic FPS speed, Link Speed, Shrines Physic bugs at (60 FPS and some at 120). Ladders at up to 90 FPS. (More to come) and Lots lots more (too many to list).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also fixes the Blackscreen present at 60 FPS caps.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also has the option to improve the haziness of the game by removing it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod can also control the Render Distance. Albeit this should be left to default in most cases.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod can also change the Handheld Internal resolution to anything you desire.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod can also turn on triple buffer (currently doesn't function on switch)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod also allows you to teleport link to the location of the camera.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;This mod can also run sequence benchmarks SIMILAR to Cyberpunk Benchmark, which outputs a file with average and 1% lows FPS. The file is located in the switch's SD card. (SDMC)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;I'M HAVING TROUBLE UNDERSTANDING HOW TO USE THIS&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Please if you are having trouble, use the &lt;a href="https://github.com/MaxLastBreath/TOTK-mods" target="_blank"&gt;TOTK Optimizer.&lt;/a&gt; It makes it a lot easier to setup.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;WHAT ELSE ARE YOU GOING TO ADD? These features will be available for &lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/maxlastbreath" target="_blank"&gt;EA.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Actor spawning.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;UI so you can change things in real time.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A console that lets you automate some fun stuff!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A way to export key frames and sequences and let's you also share it to other people!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A proper first person mode. Potentially VR (demo maybe soon?)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A partial or full mod port to BOTW, including 480 FPS cap and more...&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Slow Motion and Fast Motion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Freeze Game (AI/Time).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;First person.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lots lots lots more.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Please credit the mod if you use it for other content, preferably.&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/dark_necros/?hl=en" target="_blank"&gt;Front Page - Purah Art&lt;/a&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/ultracam_101.zip" type="application/zip"/>
